1. Decide the pizza place.
2. Decide the type of pizza I want to order 
3. Call the pizza place
4. Order the pizza 
    4a. Pay over phone 
    4b. Pay at door
5. Wait for pizza delivery 
6. Greet delivery driver
7. See step 4b if necessary
8. Make sure the pizza is hot. 
9.Tip the driver and tell him have a great day
10. Be blessed and enjoy your food. 